incident.email_body_text:
Barracuda 

Save your spot. 

View online  

Defense-in-depth strategies to protect critical Entra ID data

November 11, 2025 | 9:30am SGT | 12:30pm AEDT 

Register Now   

Hi john, 

Please join us for our webinar, "Defense-in-depth strategies to protect critical Entra ID data." 

Be part of an in-depth discussion of the risks associated with rapid, widespread adoption of Microsoft Entra ID, as well as advanced strategies for effective protection, at a new webinar coming soon.

Join us and find out why cybercriminals are targeting vulnerable Entra ID data--and to understand why the loss or compromise of that data can result in costly operational downtime.

Plus, discover the strategies and technologies— including new Barracuda backup capabilities— that you can leverage now to ensure your Entra ID data is fully protected.

Don't miss out. Reserve your spot at the webinar right now, and get the info and insights you need to secure and protect your organization's Entra ID system and data. 

Our Speaker 

Stefan van der Wal 

Principal Technical Marketing Engineer 

Barracuda Networks 

Don't wait, register today! 

Regards, 

Barracuda APAC Team

 3175 Winchester Blvd, Campbell, CA 95008, United States
